# <type>: <subject — imperative, no period, ≤ 72 chars>
#
# Allowed types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, test, chore, revert, perf, ci, style, build
#
# Body (optional, wrap at 72 chars):
# - WHY this change is needed (the motivation, not the diff)
# - WHAT user-visible behaviour changes
# - REFERENCES: ADR / issue / docs/constraints.md anchor if applicable
#
# Footer (optional):
#   Refs: #123
#   Supersedes-ADR: 0004
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <describe>
#
# Tip: enable this template once with
#   git config commit.template .gitmessage
